到熱狗同達哥FAN屎咁既LV"},{"pid":"2362d560eb84f69470b39e32de95671ca63a867a","tid":1978051,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講批鬥能力:<br />\n達哥<span style=\"color: red;\">FAN屎</span>=熱狗&gt;左膠&gt;5毛<br />\n<br />\n本身5毛係冇撚腦既, 係批鬥方面根撚本勁唔撚過某d香港人<br />\n因為香港人批鬥起上黎, 係真係可以食, 玩, 訓, 坐, 企, 走, 跑, 任何一個動作都可以搵到位入, 參考當年熱狗打爆高登, 幾十人就可以收撚左高登皮, 令高登倒台<br />\n達哥出國FIFA直播, 坐隔離既無辜PARTNER比達哥FAN屎批鬥到連<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屎</span></span>都不撚如<br />\n5毛根撚本去唔到熱狗同達哥FAN屎咁既LV</blockquote>"},{"pid":"93e2a06e045e543c67a63cd12ec80fe0f4da96db","tid":1978051,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"假如 林慧韡 好似 黃子華 咁 埋過TVB堆<br />\n<br />\n就可以攞到「TVB達哥，唔計」免死金牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2013/1220/U280P22T1D232294F1DT20131220111907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2013%2F1220%2FU280P22T1D232294F1DT20131220111907.jpg&h=55287de4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06fa2a7bf0c394ea951bd8d172237eaaaf2f08cc","tid":1978051,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"注, 熱狗金主唔一定係共產黨<br />\n只要金主係表面深藍屍或者係淺藍屍,姐係好似達哥咁, 因為要靠中國或共產黨發大財, 唔可以表態, 參與功能組別等等<br />\n你班友迫佢參與功能組別, 佢地連扮黃都冇得扮, 佢地就有動機要收你個黃色經濟圈皮"},{"pid":"268b59cbdcca89f9991260f48fa02b367fa26166","tid":1978051,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e71263b8625825216081161125bac672c6d1074a","tid":1978051